{"tid":2135432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"娛樂台知名會然勝x因為唔戴口罩做gym比人公審不勝壓力亂吐口水仲比人拉左...18+[多圖]","createTime":"2020-08-01T12:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T06:06:02.000Z","uid":52073,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b200f35f4204f5bd6d2a9d400eb5ec24c6ab60","tid":2135432,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:04:35.000Z","msg":"最近gym房又封撚左 佢好緊火成日同我做愛發洩 頭先佢終於忍唔住話要落街操野 咁我咪join佢一齊操<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n落到公園我叫佢自己開始操先 我去買啲野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知買完野食返到黎見到佢比班太極師奶圍住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話佢唔戴口罩做gym<br />\n<br />\n一開始佢都好聲好氣同班師奶理論 但班師奶太多人 一人一句佢開始頂唔順瘋了!<br />\n<br />\n開始講埋哂啲你阿媽個波罩你阿呢啲語無倫次嘅野串返班師奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢仲恐嚇班師奶叫佢地唔好明知山有虎偏向虎山行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想講...而家香港啲山邊有老虎架==<br />\n<br />\n之後班太極師奶話要為民除害...係咁用太極推手推牙利出公園...牙利就還拖狂吐佢地口水 場面極度混亂一發不可收拾...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我隔離個牙叔仲係咁拍手話 好!好武功!<br />\n而我自己就緊係坐埋一邊食野欣賞佢地嘅表演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後有2個差佬行bin經過 話佢地違反限聚令+公眾地方行為不檢拉哂佢地返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽牙利講 仲話佢因為唔戴口罩比人罰左2000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑死我<br />\n<br />\n如題...18+<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saHOeKt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsaHOeKt.jpg&h=2019c03e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ff541344fc5f6450e44be5b19b6a89d9601eeb4","tid":2135432,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:04:46.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"8c2942410789bf7bb21ca3fc11737d8aae447553","tid":2135432,"uid":202591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:10:55.000Z","msg":"=="},{"pid":"5866f948e59d28a37c6ccb106d000dcc24da7546","tid":2135432,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"樓主搞大我個肚唔認數正撲街"},{"pid":"846acd8f5c2ecfeac068053735ce3389818cd31c","tid":2135432,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5866f948e59d28a37c6ccb106d000dcc24da7546","tid":2135432,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"樓主搞大我個肚唔認數正撲街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:25:37.000Z","msg":"個仔唔係我"},{"pid":"196577a8ad5a78f0815cee19c0638711701808c1","tid":2135432,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:35:59.000Z","msg":"勝利x 叫牙利 好似有啲頭緒..."},{"pid":"998f288491b98c5ac5a5b2c9359222465532ecb7","tid":2135432,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勝x 叫牙利 好似有啲頭緒...</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6f33c4787d8768090fd18af0935e1e4b0e6570df","tid":2135432,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"998f288491b98c5ac5a5b2c9359222465532ecb7","tid":2135432,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勝x 叫牙利 好似有啲頭緒...</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T12:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yTKUatO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyTKUatO.jpg&h=f37bea74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c20939ed9a51bb69efab4b9776f4f119ad6c7ddc","tid":2135432,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score